title: Badge Without Honor (1960) Bonanza Western TV show

sources.title: Badge Without Honor (1960) Bonanza Western TV show
sources.description:
The Cartwrights grow suspicious of U.S. Deputy Marshall Gerald Eskith (Dan Duryea), assigned to escort a reluctant witness, who is also a close friend of theirs, to a racketeering trial in San Francisco.
 
Director: Arthur Lubin
Writer: John Twist
Stars: Pernell Roberts, Dan Blocker, Michael Landon
Genres: Classics, Cult, TV, Western
